fields.name: iPhone 15 Pro Max
fields.description: The iPhone 15 Pro Max is Apple's latest flagship smartphone featuring the groundbreaking A17 Bionic chip, ProMotion OLED display, and advanced triple-lens camera system with improved night mode, cinematic video, and professional photography capabilities. It boasts a premium titanium build, enhanced battery life, and superior performance for gaming, AR, and everyday multitasking.

fields.name: iPhone 15 Pro
fields.description: iPhone 15 Pro combines the power of the A17 Bionic chip with a sleek lightweight design, featuring a triple-camera system, ProMotion display for smooth visuals, and enhanced AR and photography capabilities. Ideal for users wanting top-tier Apple performance without the larger Max size.

fields.name: iPhone 15 Plus
fields.description: iPhone 15 Plus offers a 6.7-inch OLED display, improved battery life, and reliable performance with the A16 Bionic chip. Its dual-camera system captures high-quality images and videos. Supports MagSafe accessories for fast charging and attachment.

fields.name: iPhone 14 Pro Max
fields.description: iPhone 14 Pro Max features the A15 Bionic chip, 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display, and a triple-camera system. Face ID, night mode, cinematic video recording, and strong build quality make it a premium device for photography and everyday performance.

fields.name: iPhone 14 Pro
fields.description: The iPhone 14 Pro combines a sleek design with the powerful A15 Bionic chip, triple-camera system, and ProMotion display. Ideal for photography, gaming, and productivity tasks with excellent battery life and iOS ecosystem features.

fields.name: iPhone 14
fields.description: iPhone 14 offers excellent performance at an affordable price with A15 Bionic chip, dual-camera system, 6.1-inch OLED display, and iOS features. Balances efficiency, battery life, and everyday usability for Apple users.

fields.name: Galaxy S23 Ultra
fields.description: Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra features a 6.8-inch Dynamic AMOLED display, integrated S Pen stylus, Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor, and a quad-camera system capable of professional-level photography and videography. All-day battery life ensures uninterrupted usage.

fields.name: Galaxy S23+
fields.description: Galaxy S23+ offers a 6.6-inch AMOLED display, versatile triple-camera system, fast charging, and powerful Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor. Premium design and software enhancements make it ideal for Android enthusiasts.

fields.name: Galaxy S23
fields.description: Samsung Galaxy S23 is compact yet powerful, featuring a 6.1-inch AMOLED display, triple-camera system, Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor, and optimized battery life for daily productivity and photography.

fields.name: Galaxy Z Fold5
fields.description: Galaxy Z Fold5 is Samsungâ€™s foldable flagship phone with a futuristic design, large internal foldable AMOLED display, multi-tasking features, and top-of-the-line Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor. Perfect for users wanting a tablet and phone in one.

fields.name: Galaxy Z Flip5
fields.description: Galaxy Z Flip5 is a stylish foldable phone that folds into a compact size while providing a flexible 6.7-inch AMOLED main display. Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor ensures smooth performance, and its dual-camera system captures high-quality photos.

fields.name: Google Pixel 8 Pro
fields.description: Google Pixel 8 Pro delivers a pure Android experience with advanced AI-powered features, Tensor G3 processor, and a triple-camera system for professional-quality photography and videography. Sleek design and smooth display enhance user experience.

fields.name: Google Pixel 8
fields.description: Google Pixel 8 offers a pure Android experience with a dual-camera system, Tensor G3 processor, excellent battery life, and smart features like voice assistant and adaptive display. Affordable yet premium in experience.

fields.name: OnePlus 12
fields.description: OnePlus 12 is a flagship Android device with fast Snapdragon processor, OxygenOS interface for smooth multitasking, AMOLED display, and versatile camera system for photography enthusiasts. Designed for speed and performance.

fields.name: OnePlus 11
fields.description: OnePlus 11 combines powerful performance, AMOLED display, and responsive camera system at a competitive price. Ideal for Android users seeking high performance at a lower cost.

fields.name: Xiaomi 13 Pro
fields.description: Xiaomi 13 Pro features a high-resolution AMOLED display, powerful processor, advanced camera with fast charging, and MIUI enhancements. Excellent for photography, gaming, and long battery usage.

fields.name: Xiaomi 13
fields.description: Xiaomi 13 delivers strong performance, AMOLED display, dual-camera setup, and fast charging at an affordable price. Perfect for users who want a balanced smartphone experience without overspending.

fields.name: Oppo Find X6 Pro
fields.description: Oppo Find X6 Pro offers a sleek design, excellent AMOLED display, and an advanced camera system. Snapdragon processor ensures smooth performance for photography, video, and gaming.

fields.name: Oppo Reno 11 Pro
fields.description: Oppo Reno 11 Pro is a mid-range smartphone with good performance, AMOLED display, versatile cameras, and reliable battery life. Ideal for daily use and casual photography.

fields.name: Samsung Galaxy A54
fields.description: Samsung Galaxy A54 is a budget-friendly smartphone with solid performance, AMOLED display, capable camera, and long battery life. Designed for users who want reliable Android features without breaking the bank.

fields.name: MacBook Air M2 13-inch
fields.description: The MacBook Air M2 13-inch is a lightweight Apple laptop powered by the M2 chip, delivering excellent performance for everyday tasks, creative work, and multitasking. Features a Retina display, Magic Keyboard, and all-day battery life, ideal for students and professionals.

fields.name: MacBook Pro 14-inch
fields.description: MacBook Pro 14-inch combines portability with professional-grade performance powered by the M2 Pro chip. With a Liquid Retina XDR display, advanced thermal design, and long battery life, it's perfect for video editing, software development, and graphic design.

fields.name: MacBook Pro 16-inch
fields.description: MacBook Pro 16-inch offers a large Retina display, M2 Pro/Max chips, and powerful GPU options for high-end performance. Ideal for video production, 3D rendering, and professional workflows requiring maximum speed and battery life.

fields.name: Dell XPS 13
fields.description: Dell XPS 13 is a compact Windows laptop with a stunning InfinityEdge display, latest Intel processor, and solid build quality. Great for business professionals and students seeking a lightweight, high-performance device.

fields.name: Dell XPS 15
fields.description: Dell XPS 15 features a larger display, dedicated GPU options, and powerful Intel processors, making it ideal for content creators, gamers, and professionals who need both performance and portability.

fields.name: HP Spectre x360
fields.description: HP Spectre x360 is a versatile convertible laptop with touchscreen, pen support, and long battery life. Ideal for students, designers, and professionals who value portability and a premium design.

fields.name: HP Envy 15
fields.description: HP Envy 15 offers powerful performance with Intel processors, dedicated graphics, and a high-quality display. Designed for professionals, creatives, and multitaskers who need a balance of power and portability.

fields.name: Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon
fields.description: Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon is a durable business laptop with lightweight design, excellent keyboard, long battery life, and enterprise-level security features. Perfect for executives and professionals on the go.

fields.name: Lenovo Legion 5
fields.description: Lenovo Legion 5 is a gaming laptop featuring high-refresh-rate display, powerful GPU, and efficient cooling system. Ideal for gamers and creators requiring high-performance graphics and smooth gameplay.

fields.name: Lenovo IdeaPad 5
fields.description: Lenovo IdeaPad 5 is an affordable laptop for students and professionals, offering solid performance, a sleek design, and long battery life. Perfect for daily computing and productivity tasks.

fields.name: Asus ROG Strix G15
fields.description: Asus ROG Strix G15 is a gaming laptop with high-refresh display, advanced cooling, and powerful CPU/GPU combination. Optimized for gaming, streaming, and high-end graphics tasks.

fields.name: Asus ZenBook 14
fields.description: Asus ZenBook 14 is a slim and stylish ultrabook with excellent battery life, lightweight design, and full-featured ports. Perfect for professionals and students seeking a portable yet powerful device.

fields.name: Acer Swift 3
fields.description: Acer Swift 3 is a lightweight, budget-friendly laptop with solid performance, long battery life, and portability. Ideal for students, office work, and casual computing.

fields.name: Acer Predator Helios 300
fields.description: Acer Predator Helios 300 is a gaming laptop with high-performance GPU, efficient cooling system, and high-refresh display. Perfect for competitive gaming and heavy graphics tasks.

fields.name: MSI GF63 Thin
fields.description: MSI GF63 Thin is an affordable gaming laptop offering decent GPU performance, lightweight design, and good battery life. Suitable for casual gamers and students.

fields.name: Microsoft Surface Laptop 5
fields.description: Microsoft Surface Laptop 5 features a sleek design, high-resolution touchscreen, and powerful Intel processors. Ideal for business users, students, and creative professionals.

fields.name: Microsoft Surface Pro 9
fields.description: Microsoft Surface Pro 9 is a tablet-laptop hybrid with detachable keyboard, high-resolution display, and pen support. Perfect for creative professionals, students, and on-the-go productivity.

fields.name: Razer Blade 15
fields.description: Razer Blade 15 is a high-end gaming laptop with premium build quality, high-refresh display, powerful GPU options, and efficient cooling. Designed for professional gamers and content creators.

fields.name: Razer Book 13
fields.description: Razer Book 13 is a productivity-focused ultrabook with lightweight design, excellent keyboard, high-resolution display, and all-day battery life. Perfect for professionals and students.

fields.name: Samsung Galaxy Book3 Ultra
fields.description: Samsung Galaxy Book3 Ultra is a premium Windows laptop with high-resolution AMOLED display, powerful Intel processor, and solid build quality. Ideal for creators, professionals, and multimedia tasks.
